  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will track changes in oral health in pregnant women. Subjects will be assigned to
      either regular oral care or advanced oral care and be given oral care products to use until
      they deliver. A comparison between the two groups (regular and advanced oral care) will be
      made to see if the oral care products impacted oral health and maternity variables.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
